{"tid":496709,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"批摩佬戰術悶蛋 雲高爾︰我經常踢進攻足球","createTime":"2017-12-12T03:24:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-12T07:52:31.000Z","uid":122,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"660e421909fead4a4c2c9d027bd0129a3664b988","tid":496709,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T03:24:33.000Z","msg":"荷蘭名帥雲高爾（LvG）批評曼聯現任領隊摩連奴戰術悶蛋，聲稱自己帶領紅魔時踢法更加吸引。<br />\n<br />\n出任曼聯領隊兩年的雲高爾，2016年在帶領曼聯贏得其任內唯一錦標的英格蘭足總盃冠軍後兩日便辭退，球隊在2015/16球季只射入了49球，是1990年以來新低，較今季只踢了16場後的入球總數只多13球。然而任紅魔領隊期間被指戰術沉悶的LvG在荷蘭《Fox Sports》的節目中表示︰「我們的足球踢法是相當好的，但並不是在英格蘭獲欣賞的足球。然而現在看著曼聯，我要說摩連奴並沒受到批評，而這是更為悶蛋的足球。」<br />\n<br />\n強調自己與摩連奴之間沒有問題的LvG又說︰「曼聯現在踢的是防守足球，我經常踢進攻足球，證據是我們的對手通常都『泊大巴』，現在他們都那樣做了，因為摩連奴踢法是如此防守性。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/vangaal.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmetrouk2.files.wordpress.com%2F2015%2F02%2Fvangaal.gif&h=c2a5f012&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f347b37152e26fec27dc31abd20b3e7d62dbaef5","tid":496709,"uid":131176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T03:25:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一沉百踩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d4bcbc77f9dd86be64c38cc271a29bd823a8649","tid":496709,"uid":2429,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T03:26:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.anyanother.com/data/74072.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.anyanother.com%2Fdata%2F74072.jpg&h=6285fb8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c17f5663b35a0589cb83a05647ba43d2b88aa4a","tid":496709,"uid":131176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T03:27:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.anyanother.com/data/74072.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.anyanother.com%2Fdata%2F74072.jpg&h=6285fb8e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/